# SUNITA Milk Dairy (C++)

A simple **console-based C++ project** for managing basic milk dairy operations.

## Features

* Login system
* Milk deposit & bill calculation
* Animal meal purchase
* Loan calculator
* Menu-driven interface

## Technology

* C++
* Console application

## How to Run

```bash
g++ main.cpp -o dairy
./dairy
```

## Login

```
Password: 3003
```

## Purpose

This project is made for **learning C++ basics and OOP concepts**.


